data.description: Great location! This 2 story home is situated on a large fenced yard with mature trees. And offers over 2900 livable square feet!  First floor boasts warm wood work surrounding the cozy fireplace in the oversized family room.  Large formal living room or den connects to elegant dining room, great kitchen and eat in space w/sliding glass doors to access the huge deck and custom patio. Upstairs spacious primary bedroom suite features walk-in closet and  bath with double sinks. Nice sized bedrooms upstairs with full guest bath. Finished lower level for entertaining. Close to schools, shopping, dining and highway.
